---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<BaseHead title="General Learning & Revision Resources" description="Discover our curated collection of general learning and revision resources to help you study more effectively." />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body>
<Header />
<main>
<div class="resource-intro-container">
<h1>General Learning & Revision Resources</h1>
<p>
Effective learning isn't just about what you study; it's also about how you study. This section is dedicated to proven techniques and strategies that will help you become a more confident and efficient learner, regardless of the subject.
</p>
</div>

		<div class="resources-container">
			<section class="resource-section">
				<h2 class="resource-heading">Revision & Study Techniques</h2>
				<ul class="resource-list">
					<li>
						<strong>Coming Soon</strong>
						<p>Great resources on their way!</p>
						<a href="#" class="resource-link">Keep an eye out!</a>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>
			
		</div>

		<div class="cta-section">
			<h2>Need One-to-One Guidance?</h2>
			<p>Our expert tutors can provide personalized strategies and support to help you develop strong study habits. Book a free consultation to get started today!</p>
			<a href="/consultations" class="cta-button">
				Book Your Free Consultation
			</a>
		</div>
	</main>
	<Footer />
</body>
</html>

<style>
main {
color: var(--accent);
max-width: 900px;
margin: 2em auto;
padding: 0 1em;
box-sizing: border-box;
}

.resource-intro-container {
	text-align: center;
	margin-bottom: 3em;
}

.resource-intro-container h1 {
	font-size: clamp(1.8em, 5vw, 2.5em);
	margin-bottom: 0.5em;
}

.resource-intro-container p {
	max-width: 700px;
	margin: 0 auto;
	font-size: clamp(1em, 2vw, 1.1em);
	line-height: 1.7;
}

.resources-container {
	display: grid;
	gap: 2.5em;
	padding: 0 1em;
}

.resource-section {
	border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gray-light);
	padding-bottom: 2em;
}

.resource-section:last-of-type {
	border-bottom: none;
}

.resource-heading {
	font-size: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 1.8em);
	color: var(--accent);
	margin-top: 0;
	margin-bottom: 1em;
	text-align: center;
}

.resource-list {
	list-style: none;
	padding: 0;
	display: grid;
	gap: 1.5em;
}

.resource-list li {
	background-color: var(--card-bg-color);
	padding: 1.5em;
	border-radius: 12px;
	box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
	background-color: white;
}

.resource-list li strong {
	display: block;
	font-size: clamp(1.1em, 2.5vw, 1.25em);
	color: var(--accent);
	margin-bottom: 0.5em;
}

.resource-list li p {
	margin: 0 0 1em;
	font-size: clamp(1em, 2vw, 1.1em);
}

.resource-link {
	color: var(--accent-pop);
	font-weight: bold;
	text-decoration: none;
	transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.resource-link:hover {
	color: var(--accent-dark);
	text-decoration: underline;
}

/* Final CTA Section */
.cta-section {
	text-align: center;
	margin-top: 4em;
	padding: 2.5em;
	background-color: white;
	border-radius: 12px;
	box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
	color: var(--accent);
}

.cta-section h2 {
	font-size: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 1.8em);
	margin-top: 0;
	color: var(--accent);
}
.cta-section p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
}

.cta-button {
	display: inline-block;
	padding: 1em 2em;
	background-color: var(--accent-pop);
	color: white;
	font-weight: bold;
	text-decoration: none;
	border-radius: 8px;
	box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.cta-button:hover {
	transform: translateY(-5px);
	box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
	.resources-container {
		grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr);
	}
}
</style>